title: MisterMusic Show 296
description:
MisterMusic Show 296-    192 kbps MP3 stereo  2 hours -

On this episode of the MisterMusic Show, I have new music from
Wye Oak, The Mary Onettes, and another new track from the latest album by
Gardens and Villa.

Plus the 'Oldie of the Week' is an alternative hit that spent 2 weeks at number 1
in the U.S. 23 years ago during March 1991.

The MisterMusic Show is broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
